headline: FedEx exec brushes off Amazon competition concerns
summary: CCO Brie Carere said the e-commerce giant still falls behind FedEx in terms of package pickup capabilities.

headline: Spotting Winners: GXO Logistics (NYSE:GXO) And Air Freight and Logistics Stocks In Q1
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at air freight and logistics stocks, starting with GXO Logistics (NYSE:GXO).
